      <title>墨西哥总统竞选领跑者谢因鲍姆讨论特朗普和移民问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/mexican-election-claudia-sheinbaum-on-trump-migration-peso</link>
