      <title>菲律宾否认与中国就争议海域达成的协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/philippines-disowns-alleged-deal-with-china-on-disputed-sea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小费迪南德·马科斯总统政府的一名高级官员表示，中国与菲律宾前政府就南海争议问题达成的任何幕后协议都将违背国家利益，并且不再有效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/philippines-disowns-alleged-deal-with-china-on-disputed-sea</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 12:11:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>多哥投票削弱未来总统的权力，以延长现任总统的统治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/togo-vote-to-weaken-future-presidents-opens-for-incumbent-to-extend-rule</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多哥立法者通过了一部新宪法，削弱了未来国家元首的权力，但可以延长总统福雷·纳辛贝的统治。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/togo-vote-to-weaken-future-presidents-opens-for-incumbent-to-extend-rule</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 11:41:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗淡化以色列最近的袭击是“玩具”所为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/middle-east-conflict-iran-says-latest-israel-counterattack-more-like-toys</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗外长在评论中将以色列在周五早些时候的袭击中使用的无人机比作“玩具”，旨在淡化袭击伊朗领土的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/middle-east-conflict-iran-says-latest-israel-counterattack-more-like-toys</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 11:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度 Deepfake 告诉我们有关全球选举安全的信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-ai-election-security-deepfakes/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[制造深度造假从未如此简单或便宜，引发了人们对世界各地民意调查可能受到损害以及对选举制度的信任受到破坏的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/features/2024-ai-election-security-deepfakes/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 11:00:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
